
You touch the symbol and seek within...


              The seventh symbol -   Casting ----

  The power you possess stems from within your minds eye, and thus
it is imperative to maintain a clear and open mind in order to
draw upon your power.  Those whose minds are cluttered will
struggle and suffer.  An ultimate mastery of power will allow
you to harnass your abilities flawlessly.  Those who display
their bravery will also reflect this clarity of mind.

